oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hank Thompson - Here's To Veterans radio program
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Hank Thompson hosts and performs on the Here's To Veterans radio show with the Brazos Valley Boys, including acoustic guitar, electric guitar, accordion, fiddle, bass and percussion.
